data.description: Welcome to 530 Old Cedartown Road, a charming house that is now available for sale! This property offers a comfortable and peaceful living experience in a quiet area. Located conveniently close to schools, shopping centers, and all essential amenities, this home provides the perfect balance between tranquility and accessibility.  Featuring three bedrooms and two bathrooms, this house is ideal for families or individuals seeking a cozy yet spacious living space. With ample parking space for up to five vehicles, you'll never have to worry about finding a spot for your cars or guests.  Step inside and be greeted by an entertainment-style home design that is sure to impress. The large kitchen is the heart of this home, complete with a generous breakfast bar, white soft-close cabinets, and beautiful pine wood countertops. All appliances have been recently updated, ensuring that you have everything you need to create culinary masterpieces.  Notable updates include a brand new roof and energy-efficient heating and air system, providing comfort and peace of mind for years to come. Situated on over an acre of private land, this property offers plenty of room for outdoor activities and relaxation. Additionally, two entry points provide convenient access from different directions.  The side car garage offers additional storage space while the laundry room has been moved to the garage, creating more room inside the house. The old laundry room has been transformed into an extra pantry and storage room with direct access to the backyard.  The layout of this home has been thoughtfully designed with entertainment in mind, ensuring that every gathering will be memorable. Smaller rooms offer versatility and can be used as bedrooms or office spaces according to your needs.  Priced competitively for a quick sale, this property won't stay on the market for long. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful house your new home. Schedule a viewing today and start envisioning your future in this delightful property!
